  \ be <italic>oxidized</italic>.  A mnemonic to help remember  the definitions is\
  \ OIL RIG (oxidized is less; reduced is gained).  It is important to note that molecules\
  \ will often contain  both ionic and covalent bonds.  Sodium hydroxide (lye, NaOH)\
